      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Conversion table:\n1 byte = 8 bits\n1 hex digit = 4 bits --> [0 - 9] [A - F]* \n*(10 - 15)\n\nExample: 16 = 0x0010\nExample 31 = 0x001F\n\nCAN ASSUME THAT THE PACKET'S METADATA IS UNSIGNED",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Conversion table:\n1 byte = 8 bits\n1 hex digit = 4 bits --> [0 - 9] [A - F]* \n*(10 - 15)\n\nExample: 16 = 0x0010\nExample 31 = 0x001F\n\nCAN ASSUME THAT THE PACKET'S METADATA IS UNSIGNED",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
